# Root Kaggle Intake

- Files in root `kaggle_intake/` are task intake files for the whole workspace.
- Build a global brief first.
- Update root memory docs before deep implementation work:
  - `rules/memory/USER_PROMPTS_LOG.md`
  - `RESEARCH_JOURNAL.md`
- Choose or create an isolated owning subproject.
- Route local engineering and local theory work into that subproject's own team.
- Never confuse this folder with local project baseline/reference stores.
